[SDG-FETCH]: run sdgfetch to display system info with your selected logo and preset
[SDG-FETCH]: sdgfetch-conf lets you pick logos and presets interactively with live previews
[SDG-FETCH]: add custom logos by placing PNG/JPG images in ~/.config/SDG-FETCH/src/ and running sdgfetch-conf
[SDG-FETCH]: sdgfetch <yourdistro> shows a themed display using distro-specific colors

